The politician was confirmed dead at Muhimbili National Hospital in Dar es Salaam late Friday. Before his retirement, the late Kandoro had been a Regional Commissioner for Tabora, Arusha, Mwanza, Dar es Salaam and Mbeya. "We have lost a very important person whose contribution as a public servant in the capacity of district, regional commissioner and council executive director will never be forgotten," the statement quoted the President. He has directed Iringa Regional Commissioner, Ms Amina Masenza to send his condolences to Kandoro's family.